- Endpoint-uri compatibile OpenAI, Anthropic etc.
- Lista completă de integrări: docs.ollama.com/integrations

SLIDE 10 — Modelele Ollama: catalog, local vs remote, ce-i pe laptop
- Catalogul: ollama.com/library
